# 🚀 Doorstep Device Repair — Enhancement Plan (2026 Edition)

## Current State Audit

After reviewing the entire codebase, here is what's **already built and working**:

| Area | Status | Details |
|---|---|---|
| **Auth** | ✅ Complete | Email OTP + Technician password login, JWT, role-based guards |
| **Customer Order Flow** | ✅ Complete | Device select → Brand grid → Create order → Live tracking → Feedback |
| **Technician Portal** | ✅ Complete | Dashboard, new orders, accept flow, status pipeline, Google Maps directions |
| **Real-time Events** | ✅ Complete | SSE-based order-available/accepted/update with toast notifications |
