- Messages stored in a new `ChatMessage` Prisma model with `orderId`, `senderId`, `senderRole`, `content`, `createdAt`
- SSE integration: emit `chat-message` events through the existing `EventsService` for real-time delivery

##### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///d:/Work/App/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Add `ChatMessage` model linked to `Order`

