- Full chat UI with message bubbles, timestamp, auto-scroll, unread badge
- Connected via SSE for real-time messages
- Accessible from the tracking page via the existing "Message" button
- Route: `/order/chat/:orderId`

##### [MODIFY] [track-order.ts](file:///d:/Work/App/mobile-service/src/app/order/track-order/track-order.ts)
- Wire the "Message" button to navigate to `/order/chat/:orderId`
